getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
select t.`name` as `NAMe` from ( select t.TITLE AS `name`, t.id,'bug' as type from zt_bug t union
select t.TITLE AS `name`,t.id,'story' as type from zt_story t union
select t.`name`,t.id,'task' as type from zt_task t ) t where t.id = ? and t.type = ?
